---
description: Best practices for accessibility in TYPO3 projects
globs: **/*.{html,php}
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use ARIA roles and attributes to enhance accessibility for assistive technologies.
- Ensure sufficient color contrast for text to improve readability.
- Provide keyboard navigation for all interactive elements.
- Use focus styles to indicate the focus state of elements.
- Implement landmarks (e.g., <nav>, <main>, <aside>) to aid screen reader navigation.
